						<p>On the pillar inside the Varadarājaśvāmi temple.</p>						

						<p>1590 A.D.</p>						

						<p>It is dated Śaka 1512, Vijaya, Chaitra, śu. 10, Thursday. The cyclic year is Vīkriti.</p>						

